-- Harel Freres of Mauritius Makes Offer for Saint Andre Sugar Estate Company
-- Ana Monteiro
-- 2010-07-13T10:20:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/harel-freres-of-mauritius-makes-offer-for-saint-andre-sugar-estate-company.html

          
          
             Harel Freres Ltd., which produces 75
percent of Mauritius’s processed sugar, made an offer for Saint
Andre Sugar Estate Co. Ltd.  
 Harel Freres would issue new shares to Saint Andre
shareholders, the company said in a statement published on the
website of the Port Louis-based stock exchange today. The
transaction may take one of several forms, subject to
conditions.  
 Shareholders should exercise caution when trading Harel
Freres’ stock, the company said.  
          
          


  


        